FBIS4-60411 "drnes101_l_94007" FBIS-NES-94-101 Daily Report 24 May 1994 ISRAEL Jericho Closure To Allow Palestinian Reorganization Jericho Closure To Allow Palestinian Reorganization TA2405142894 Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew 1400 GMT 24 May 94 TA2405142894 Tel Aviv IDF Radio Hebrew BFN [Text] Major General Ilan Biran, commander of Central Command, today decided to impose a closure on Jericho to allow the heads of the Palestinian police in the city to organize. The IDF [Israel Defense Forces] wishes to make sure that all the Palestinian policemen stationed in the city are clear on their authorities and powers pertaining to Israeli citizens traveling inside Jericho. The decision came in the wake of a series of incidents over the past few days, including this morning's incident.
